Class ChineseGrammaticalRelations

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.nlp.trees.international.pennchinese.ChineseGrammaticalRelations

  • public class ChineseGrammaticalRelations
extends java.lang.Object
    ChineseGrammaticalRelations is a set of GrammaticalRelation objects for the Chinese language. Examples are from CTB_001.fid

    Galen Andrew, Pi-Chuan Chang, Huihsin Tseng, Marie-Catherine de Marneffe
